        "body": "## Fix Footer Navigation Issue\r\n\r\n### Overview\r\nThis PR fixes an issue where all footer links were redirecting users to the Home page instead of navigating to their respective pages.\r\n\r\n### Changes Made\r\n- Updated footer link routes to point to the correct pages.\r\n- Removed incorrect `/#` links that caused navigation to always return to the homepage.\r\n- Ensured each footer item navigates to its intended route.\r\n\r\n### Affected Components\r\n- `Footer` component\r\n\r\n### Testing\r\n- Verified that each footer link correctly navigates to its respective page.\r\n- Tested locally on `localhost:3000`.\r\n- Confirmed no navigation regression on other pages.\r\n\r\n### Related Issue\r\nCloses #8 ",
